name: Worms Among Us
description: WORMS it's a memecoin token that will have it's own comic series, and collection of NFT's. It's created on the Solana blockchain through Pump.Fun. The purpose it's to create a transparent and honest coin, with the idea of bringing trust to the holders. The storyline it's being crafted along with a Literature Proffesor from the Melbourne University. All of our designs and art it's done on paper first, and then just for colour it's bring into a computer.
